text: Dayo Oyewusi (born c. 1966) is a Nigerian badminton player. She competed in 1994 Commonwealth Games in Victoria, Canada. She won the 1991 Kenya International tournament in the women's doubles event partnered with Obiageli Olorunsola. == Achievements == === IBF International === Women's singles {| class="sortable wikitable" style="font-size: 90%;" !
